description: Today I was hunting in Vinohrady, a trendy part of Prague with loads of shops and restaurants. After about 20 minutes I still didn´t  find today´s Mr.Right but I noticed a friendly guy working in a small Bistro. He didn´t seem to busy and as he had an amazing smile I decided to try my luck. He was worried about my cam as he was sure that his boss wouldn´t allow someone to film inside. So I had to pretend that I switched it off. He was not really talkative but I still found out that his salary was very bad. I told him that I make castings for a model-agency and that I look for someone "Italian-style". And when I asked him if he ever had experience with modeling he told me that one time he took part in an erotic photo-shooting. Bingo. Now guess who the story continued...
title: Czech Hunter 197
